{% block after_description %}
## Examples

Run with the CARD database for antimicrobial resistance gene detection:

```bash
bactopia --wf abricate \
  --bactopia /path/to/your/bactopia/results \
  --abricate_db card
```

Run with VFDB for virulence factor screening:

```bash
bactopia --wf abricate \
  --bactopia /path/to/your/bactopia/results \
  --abricate_db vfdb
```

:::tip
You can run this workflow multiple times with different databases to screen
against all of them. Each run will produce separate results that can be
compared.
:::

